data.description: Welcome to this 4 bed, 2 bath beauty on 1 full acre in S Harris County! The interior has LVP flooring throughout, adding elegance & durability. The separate dining area is perfect for hosting formal gatherings, while the quartz countertops & SS appliances in the kitchen are a culinary haven. 2 fireplaces, 1 in the separate living area & another in the den, create cozy focal points for gathering w/ loved ones. The vaulted ceiling in the primary bed adds an extra touch of grandeur, while the ensuite bath features desirable amenities like a separate shower, separate tub, & double vanity. The exterior amenities include a 2-car detached carport, inviting covered patio, & a stunning in-ground pool, perfect for enjoying outdoor leisure time. Additionally, the outdoor detached storage provides convenient space for storing tools & equipment. This property offers a harmonious blend of modern amenities & timeless charm, providing a truly exceptional living experience for its fortunate new owners.
